sources.title: Payday (1944)
sources.description: Payday is an animated short film, directed by Friz Freleng and first released in September, 1944. It is part of the Private Snafu series. As in all the Snafu films, the voice of Private Snafu is performed by Mel Blanc. Watch on RetroFlix.org:Â  https://retroflix.org/payday-1944/
